Package org.drip.regression.curvejacobian

Class CurveJacobianRegressionEngine

java.lang.Object
org.drip.regression.core.RegressionEngine
org.drip.regression.curvejacobian.CurveJacobianRegressionEngine
public class CurveJacobianRegressionEngine
extends RegressionEngine
CurveJacobianRegressionEngine implements the RegressionEngine for the curve Jacobian regression. It adds the CashJacobianRegressorSet, the EDFJacobianRegressorSet, the IRSJacobianRegressorSet, and the DiscountCurveJacobianRegressorSet, and launches the regression engine.

  • Module = Computational Core Module
  • Library = Computation Support
  • Project = Regression Engine Core and the Unit Regressors
  • Package = Curve Jacobian Reconciliation Regression Engine


Author:
Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
